'''2014年纽约警官被杀案件'''是指[[美国东部时间|美国东部时间]]2014年12月20日下午2点47分，在美国纽约市[[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]{{le|贝德福德·斯泰福斯特街区|Bedford–Stuyvesant, Brookly}}，两名[[纽约警察局|纽约警察局]]警官被蓄意枪击身亡。28岁的凶手伊斯迈伊尔·阿卜杜拉·布林斯利在行凶后逃入纽约地铁站自杀。<ref name=nyt141221/> 该案件被认为是針對此前的[[邁克爾·布朗命案|邁克爾·布朗命案]]（[[密苏里州|密苏里州]][[聖路易斯縣_(密蘇里州)|圣路易斯县]][[弗格森_(密蘇里州)|弗格森]]）及[[埃里克·加纳死亡案|埃里克·加纳死亡案]]（紐約市）的报复行为。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nypost.com/2014/12/20/2-nypd-cops-shot-execution-style-in-brooklyn/|title=Gunman executes 2 NYPD cops as ‘revenge’ for Garner|work=New York Post|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2015-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106181431/http://nypost.com/2014/12/20/2-nypd-cops-shot-execution-style-in-brooklyn/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/nypd-cops-assassinated-brooklyn-ambush/story?id=27738835|title=Two NYPD Cops 'Assassinated' in Brooklyn Ambush|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2015-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411125008/http://abcnews.go.com/US/nypd-cops-assassinated-brooklyn-ambush/story?id=27738835|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=nyt141221>{{cite web|last1=Mueller|first1=Benjamin|last2=Baker|first2=Al|title=Two N.Y.P.D. Officers Are Killed in Brooklyn Ambush; Suspect Commits Suicide|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/21/nyregion/two-police-officers-shot-in-their-patrol-car-in-brooklyn.html|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=December 20, 2014|accessdate=December 21, 2014|archive-date=2015-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107171814/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/21/nyregion/two-police-officers-shot-in-their-patrol-car-in-brooklyn.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
本案件发生的几周前，[[大陪审团|大陪审团]]判决不起诉纽约市警察局警官丹尼尔·潘塔里奥（Daniel Pantaleo），丹尼尔·潘塔里奥此前因为在2014年7月17日在纽约街头执勤时对被害人[[埃里克·加纳|埃里克·加纳]]（Eric Garner）的行为致其身亡。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2014/12/03/chokehold-grand-jury/19804577/| author=Melanie Eversley and Mike James| title=No charges in NYC chokehold death; federal inquiry launched| newspaper=USA Today| date=December 4, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108164228/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2014/12/03/chokehold-grand-jury/19804577/| dead-url=no}}</ref> 大陪审团的这个判决引起了纽约市内的多次抗议示威活动，以及对警方暴力执法、缺乏问责机制而興起的全國性反对浪潮。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2014/dec/13/marchers-protest-police-brutality-new-york-washington-boston| author=Lauren Gambino, Steven W Thrasher and Kayla Epstein| title=Thousands march to protest against police brutality in major US cities| newspaper=The Guardian| date=December 14, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-07| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107060303/http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2014/dec/13/marchers-protest-police-brutality-new-york-washington-boston| dead-url=no}}</ref>这次的抗议活动时逢[[密苏里州|密苏里州]][[聖路易斯縣_(密蘇里州)|圣路易斯县]][[弗格森_(密蘇里州)|弗格森]]发生{{le|弗格森骚乱事件|2014 Ferguson unrest}}，后者也肇因於大陪审团决定不起诉警官达伦·威尔逊（Darren Wilson），此人在2014年8月9日时射杀了[[邁克爾·布朗槍擊案|迈克尔·布朗]]。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/25/us/ferguson-darren-wilson-shooting-michael-brown-grand-jury.html| author=MONICA DAVEY and JULIE BOSMAN| title=Protests Flare After Ferguson Police Officer Is Not Indicted| newspaper=New York Times| date=November 24, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2018-02-01| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180201191304/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/25/us/ferguson-darren-wilson-shooting-michael-brown-grand-jury.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 案情 ==
在凶手伊斯迈伊尔·阿卜杜拉·布林斯利搭乘公共汽车抵达[[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]之前，他曾在[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[巴爾的摩|巴尔的摩市]]{{le|奥因斯米尔斯|Owings Mills, Maryland}}的郊区射傷自己的前女友莎妮卡·妮可·汤普森（Shaneka Nicole Thompson）。而致使两位警官身亡的枪击发生在{{le|默特尔大道|Myrtle Avenue}}和汤普金斯大道的一个繁忙十字路口，该路口在布鲁克林区靠近汤普金斯公共住宅。<ref name=nyt141221/> 布林斯利靠近了一辆[[警車|警車]]的侧窗位置，当时坐在车内的是布鲁克林第84分局的警官[[刘文健|刘文健]]和拉斐尔·拉莫斯（Rafael Ramos）。之后布林斯利掏出一把半自动手枪向两位警官射击多次，子弹命中二人的头部和上身，并使二人当场身亡。在纽约警局派出警力到场追捕他时，布林斯利逃入[[紐約地鐵G線|紐約地鐵G線]]的{{le|美特尔-威洛比大道站（IND跨城线）|Myrtle–Willoughby Avenues (IND Crosstown Line)}}，根据警方陈述，他在站内使用手枪自杀身亡。<ref name=nyt141221/>

== 受害人 ==
=== 刘文健 ===
刘文健（Randy Law，1982年4月8日－2014年12月20日），美籍华人，出生于中国广东省[[台山市|台山市]]。12岁时随父母移民到美国，是家里的独子。<ref name=":0">Josh Gardner, [http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2893263/Grieving-father-slain-NYPD-officer-Wenjian-Liu-speaks-time-tragic-double-cop-killing.html "Grieving father of slain NYPD officer Wenjian Liu speaks out for the first time since tragic double cop killing"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2893263/Grieving-father-slain-NYPD-officer-Wenjian-Liu-speaks-time-tragic-double-cop-killing.html |date=20150103093645 }}, ''[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]'', 1 January 2015</ref>他在纽约市警察局已工作7年，是位经验丰富的警官。他在2014年10月刚与妻子结婚，膝下无子。<ref name=":0" /><ref name="Miami Herald">{{cite news| url=http://www.miamiherald.com/news/nation-world/article4852062.html| title=Key developments in case of 2 slain NYPD officers| newspaper=Miami Herald| date=December 23, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2014-12-23| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141223091249/http://www.miamiherald.com/news/nation-world/article4852062.html| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/slain-nypd-officers-wenjian-liu-and-rafael-ramos-were-partners-1419139850|title=Slain NYPD Officers Rafael Ramos and Wenjian Liu Remembered|date=December 21, 2014|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2015-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113033252/http://www.wsj.com/articles/slain-nypd-officers-wenjian-liu-and-rafael-ramos-were-partners-1419139850|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.newsday.com/news/new-york/officers-wen-jian-liu-rafael-ramos-took-different-paths-to-nypd-1.9735342|title=Officers Wen Jian Liu, Rafael Ramos took different paths to NYPD|newspaper=Newsday|date=December 20, 2014|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2014-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222061525/http://www.newsday.com/news/new-york/officers-wen-jian-liu-rafael-ramos-took-different-paths-to-nypd-1.9735342|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 拉斐尔·拉莫斯 ===
拉斐尔·拉莫斯（Rafael Ramos，1974年12月9日－2014年12月20日），在{{le|皇后区格伦代尔|Glendale, Queens}}长期居住。他加入纽约警察局后曾担任学校保卫处探员，在2012年1月被晋升为警官。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/nypd-officers-rafael-ramos-wenjian-liu-remembered-community/story?id=27757097| author=Dan Good| title=Slain NYPD Officers Remembered for Community, Family Dedication| publisher=ABC News| date=December 22, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106143359/http://abcnews.go.com/US/nypd-officers-rafael-ramos-wenjian-liu-remembered-community/story?id=27757097| dead-url=no}}</ref>他已婚并有两个儿子。拉斐尔·拉莫斯在他的教会--皇后区格伦代尔的基督教礼拜堂里很活跃。<ref name="Miami Herald"/>他曾就读于神学院，才刚完成培训课程，成为一名志愿牧师。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/nypd-officer-ramos-killed-one-hour-chaplain-graduation-ceremony-n273546| author=Shamar Walters| title=NYPD Officer Ramos Killed One Hour Before Chaplain Graduation Ceremony| publisher=NBC News| date=December 23, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-05| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150105000156/http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/nypd-officer-ramos-killed-one-hour-chaplain-graduation-ceremony-n273546| dead-url=no}}</ref>他曾计划自己要在卸下警職后投入教會。

=== 莎妮卡·妮可·汤普森 ===
莎妮卡·妮可·汤普森（Shaneka Nicole Thompson，事发时29岁），事发当天的大量媒体报道中并没有提及她亦为同一案件的受害人。汤普森是本案凶手的前女友，亦在案發當天被其射中腹部，但幸运地活了下来、情况稳定。警方在對她的讯问中得知：案发同日，布林斯利曾去找她，两人发生了争执。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/21/us/new-york-police-officers-shot/| author=Ashley Fantz, Josh Berlinger and Shimon Prokupecz| title=NYC cop killer had criminal record and angry social media posts, police say| publisher=CNN| date=December 21, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-08| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108230311/http://www.cnn.com/2014/12/21/us/new-york-police-officers-shot| dead-url=no}}</ref>布林斯利想拿手枪自杀但被汤普森阻止，最后布林斯利向汤普森开枪并离开前往布鲁克林。<ref name="Kim Barker, Mosi Secret, and Richard Fausset">{{cite news| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/03/nyregion/ismaaiyl-brinsleys-many-identities-fueled-life-of-wrong-turns.html| author=Kim Barker, Mosi Secret, and Richard Fausset| title=Many identities of New York officers’ killer in a life of wrong turns| publisher=New York Times| date=January 3, 2015| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-06| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106083817/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/03/nyregion/ismaaiyl-brinsleys-many-identities-fueled-life-of-wrong-turns.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>在射傷汤普森后，布林斯利曾打电话给汤普森的母亲和其他家人，并称枪击是个意外。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/ismaaiyl-brinsley-suspected-of-shooting-new-york-police-had-criminal-history-ties-to-brooklyn-1419188892| author=Rebecca Davis O’Brien, Pervaiz Shallwani and Scott Calvert| title=Ismaaiyl Brinsley Led Life of Trouble Before Attack| newspaper=Wall Street Journal| date=December 21, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109013542/http://www.wsj.com/articles/ismaaiyl-brinsley-suspected-of-shooting-new-york-police-had-criminal-history-ties-to-brooklyn-1419188892| dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 凶手 ==
'''伊斯梅尔·阿卜杜拉·布林斯利'''（Ismaaiyl Abdullah Brinsley，1986年10月31日－2014年12月20日）在案发前有长期犯罪历史，并被家人所疏远。他出生在纽约市布鲁克林区的一个穆斯林非洲裔美国人的家庭。他曾因为拥有武器和抢劫罪被逮捕，其中在乔治亚州州和俄亥俄州共有19次被捕的记录。在乔治亚州，他曾犯下持有武器的重罪，而且在案发前，他本人仍居住在該州。<ref name=nyt141220>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/21/nyregion/police-combing-through-shooting-suspects-arrest-history-and-violent-day.html|title=Police Combing Through Shooting Suspect’s Arrest History and Violent Day|date=December 20, 2014|author=J. David Goodman|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2015-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150107171819/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/21/nyregion/police-combing-through-shooting-suspects-arrest-history-and-violent-day.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=wsj141221>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/ismaaiyl-brinsley-suspected-of-shooting-new-york-police-had-criminal-history-ties-to-brooklyn-1419188892|title=Ismaaiyl Brinsley Led Life of Trouble Before Attack|date=December 21, 2014|author=Rebecca Davis O’Brien|newspaper=Wall Street Journal|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109013542/http://www.wsj.com/articles/ismaaiyl-brinsley-suspected-of-shooting-new-york-police-had-criminal-history-ties-to-brooklyn-1419188892|dead-url=no}}</ref>布林斯利一年前曾试图自杀。<ref name=wsj141221/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/pal-ismaaiyl-brinsley-describes-smart-transient-man-article-1.2052537|title=Cop killer Ismaaiyl Brinsley had a long criminal record, was violent and suicidal, and frightened his mom: police|date=December 21, 2014|newspaper=The New York Daily News|author=Barry Paddock|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2015-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109013544/http://www.nydailynews.com/new-york/pal-ismaaiyl-brinsley-describes-smart-transient-man-article-1.2052537|dead-url=no}}</ref> 案发当天，他在杀死警察之前曾试图用自己的枪支自杀，但他在女友劝说下放弃後，却反而向女友开枪。<ref name="Kim Barker, Mosi Secret, and Richard Fausset"/> 从女友那里离开后，他曾在自己的[[Instagram|Instagram]]帐号上發帖，表示將對埃里克·加纳和迈克尔·布朗兩起命案進行报复，公開了弒警意图。随后他乘坐巴士前往纽约市的途中，他发出的信息写到：「今天我要把翅膀插到猪身上……他们弄死我们中的一个……让我弄死他们兩個……就像那样」（I'm putting Wings on Pigs Today ... They Take 1 of Ours ... Lets Take 2 of Theirs. {{sic}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/two-new-york-city-police-officers-are-shot-and-killed-in-a-brazen-ambush-in-brooklyn/2014/12/20/2a73f7ae-8898-11e4-9534-f79a23c40e6c_story.html|title=Two New York City police officers are shot and killed in a brazen ambush in Brooklyn|date=December 20, 2014|accessdate=December 21, 2014|newspaper=Washington Post|author=Peter Holley|archive-date=2015-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106115956/http://www.washingtonpost.com/national/two-new-york-city-police-officers-are-shot-and-killed-in-a-brazen-ambush-in-brooklyn/2014/12/20/2a73f7ae-8898-11e4-9534-f79a23c40e6c_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后[[巴尔的摩警察局|巴尔的摩警察局]]追踪到布林斯利从巴尔的摩到纽约的行踪，并给纽约警察局发出一份昭示了其意图的传真；这份传真在案发前的1分钟发抵纽约。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/future_tense/2014/12/21/baltimore_county_police_sent_a_fax_and_teletype_message_to_the_new_york.html|title=Baltimore County police sent a fax and teletype message to the New York Police department.|work=Slate Magazine|accessdate=2015-01-06|archive-date=2015-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106102825/http://www.slate.com/blogs/future_tense/2014/12/21/baltimore_county_police_sent_a_fax_and_teletype_message_to_the_new_york.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布林斯利据称与美国的监狱黑帮{{le|黑色游击队家族|Black Guerrilla Family}}有勾結，根据警方线人的情报，该黑帮曾打算对警察进行报复攻击。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/killer-nypd-slays-ran-black-guerrilla-family-article-1.2052069| author=Tina Moore and Bill Hutchinson| title=Police believe New York City cop killer was a member of the Black Guerrilla Family: sources| newspaper=New York Daily News| date=December 20, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109013542/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/national/killer-nypd-slays-ran-black-guerrilla-family-article-1.2052069| dead-url=no}}</ref>但据一位匿名的联邦执法线人引述，两者并没有明显的关系。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/20/ismaaiyl-brinsley-nypd-black-guerilla-family_n_6361324.html| author=Igor Bobic| title=Feds Deny NYPD Cop Killer Had Ties To Black Guerilla Family Prison Gang| work=Huffington Post| date=December 21, 2014| accessdate=2015-01-06| archive-date=2015-01-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150109013542/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/20/ismaaiyl-brinsley-nypd-black-guerilla-family_n_6361324.html| dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 回应 ==
=== 官方 ===
